reviews.review_text: only digital aud source Hi GD folks,   yes,  this is another only exclusive digital audience source by Jeff Silberman who hauled in a PCM machine, cables , etc.; a testament of the dedication to capture the whole sound of a concert, the hall, crowd, and of course the band from the stage being in front of the sound board aka FOB "front of board" - this is a great example.  Nice clear , well defined and great dynamic range that only the Grateful Dead can deliver complete with the occasional "Phil Bomb". This whole Philly run seems to be exceptional and the highlight of spring 1984... if you have a really good sound system you will enjoy this show ... download worthy  and big thanks to Miller and Co. for the diligent  transfer work.  GD RULES !!!
